OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779711071
OL,3,CRed Arrows to reduce display team size
OL,5,FThe Red Arrows - based at RAF
OL,6,FWaddington in Lincolnshire - will fly
OL,7,Fwith seven aircraft rather than nine
OL,8,Ffor most displays moving forward as
OL,9,Fthe fleet transitions "to a future
OL,10,Faircraft type".
OL,12,FAn RAF spokesperson said: "The Red
OL,13,FArrows are the pride of the nation,
OL,14,Fknown globally for their world-class
OL,15,Fprecision, speed, and teamwork.
OL,17,F"The Red Arrows will fly in a nine-
OL,18,Faircraft formation for HM The King's
OL,19,FBirthday Flypast and the 4th of July
OL,20,F250 Commemorations in the USA this
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,26,@qD@WOUrD@NO]tD@[OU
