FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779711071
OL,3,CRed Arrows to reduce display team size
OL,5,F"For other displays, they will operate
OL,6,Fwith seven aircraft, continuing to
OL,7,Fdeliver high-quality, engaging
OL,8,Fdisplays at air shows and events
OL,9,Facross the UK, mainland Europe and
OL,10,Ffurther afield.
OL,12,F"This will support the sustainable
OL,13,Fmanagement of the Hawk T1 fleet and
OL,14,Fprepare the team for a transition to a
OL,15,Ffuture aircraft type."
OL,17,FIn 2021, the government extended the
OL,18,Fout-of-service date for the Red Arrows
OL,19,FHawk T1 aircraft, which have performed
OL,20,Fnearly 4,000 displays worldwide, to
OL,21,F2030.
OL,26,@mD@AOUtD@AOUwD@VO]
