CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1779711071
OL,3,CRed Arrows to reduce display team size
OL,5,FHawk T1 aircraft require substantial
OL,6,Fmaintenance, with spare parts and
OL,7,Fcritical components, particularly
OL,8,Fengines, becoming less readily
OL,9,Favailable over time.
OL,11,FThe Red Arrows regularly flew seven
OL,12,Faircraft in the 1960s and display
OL,13,Fseasons comprising seven aircraft were
OL,14,Falso flown in 2012 and 2022.
OL,16,FThe display team will be seen at air
OL,17,Fshows and events across the UK,
OL,18,Fmainland Europe and further afield
OL,19,Ffrom May to October this year.
